extends layout

block content
  p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the MDN.

  img(src='/images/books.svg' height='200vh' alt='book logo')

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The #[span(style='color:#a23425;') library] has the following record counts:

    ul
      li.nostyle #[strong Books:] !{data.book_count}
      li.nostyle #[strong Copies:] !{data.bookInstance_count}
      li.nostyle #[strong Copies available:] !{data.bookInstance_available_count}
      li.nostyle #[strong Author:] !{data.author_count}
      li.nostyle #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}